        <num>44-12-282</num>
        <content>
          <p>Annually, the councilmembers shall elect a chairperson for a term of one year.The council shall meet as frequently as needed to perform its duties, upon the call of the council chairperson.Five councilmembers shall constitute a quorum to conduct business.</p>
